'''Madro<U+00F1>era''' is a municipality located in the [[C<U+00E1>ceres (province)|province of C<U+00E1>ceres]], [[Extremadura]], [[Spain]]. According to the [[2006]] [[census]] ([[Instituto Nacional de Estad<U+00ED>stica (Spain)|INE]]), the municipality has a population of 2910 inhabitants.

